Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.85,0:00:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.03,0:00:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.77,0:00:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是比作为火炬被遗忘要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.12,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是留给了池他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.44,0:02:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你们不会渐渐淡忘了我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最终...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜会记得我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.10,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此我就心满意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.93,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.44,0:02:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 去哪里了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.87,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.15,0:02:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马 马上给你准备换洗的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点进屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.65,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是火炬的你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是错觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为布局而放置的火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被人熄灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要引我现身的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该更加大肆地成片地熄灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.19,0:03:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的计划中要用到火炬这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士应该还没注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 玛丽安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让人妨碍到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管对方是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.56,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 吉田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好 池同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.06,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 坂井同学呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 还没见着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.08,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.94,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找坂井有事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学 不是你想的那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是碰巧爸爸给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是电影票什么的就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这种也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放学后有空吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.08,0:05:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要紧的事倒是没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 吉田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被谁放了鸽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在找一起去的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.91,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 其实我有两张美术展的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.69,0:06:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果今天放学后有时间的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始上课了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.21,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.09,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就遇到讨厌的家伙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那么狠狠地揍了一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼眼的小丫头暂时不会露面了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.79,0:06:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 接下来就是作为主菜的“拾尸者”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点找到 撕咬嚼碎他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.78,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个熟悉这城市的人带路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢花痴且年轻力壮的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 混蛋马可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.68,0:07:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这两个家伙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比于爱好而言还是选择年轻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我们 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别多管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了彩可别怪我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂彩的不是你们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.93,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 田中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以称呼你“大姐”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 去不去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后啊 放学后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.50,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且难得的票不去就浪费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得和秘器太过疏远了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找到徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始你们得四处搜寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们具体该做些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 先回答我的提问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.05,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是这个城市里的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.69,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.03,0:09:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.57,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这个城市有没有发生大的事件或事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及奇怪的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不看报纸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的也不过是些交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.08,0:09:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉有点不对劲 这城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽安就待在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是败给了“悼词诵读者”的缘故吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件也不过就是偷窃之类啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么出人意料的事件吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么刚才解说的“火炬”明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道其大量集结的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.07,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个城市人最多的地方是哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...是这前面的车站附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.93,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来只能进行地毯式搜查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍白色火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那难道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“猎人”法利亚格尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.74,0:11:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先在这里等一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近应该有什么人在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是“猎人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到是条大鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没逮住麻雀倒抓住了鹰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情况下杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没 怎么可能会有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我锋利的牙玛乔里·冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“猎人”又活动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“悼词诵读者”正赶过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.38,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的你来说很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有其它该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的 的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.33,0:12:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面展出的好像是彩色玻璃画窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世之徒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没打算把你带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.33,0:13:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢随意破坏世界平衡的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微谈谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.24,0:14:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“悼词诵读者”玛乔里·冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及“蹂躏之爪牙”马可西亚斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“猎人”法利亚格尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的火雾战士原来是你们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但捣乱的难道是你们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.11,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是现在才开始动手干掉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.04,0:14:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来被不识风趣的入侵者逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.64,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“猎人”那家伙在追的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.38,0:14:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了 虽然说实话没空理会讨灭的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.36,0:14:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在还没绊倒前踢掉石子也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想要对我的猎物下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被撕咬嚼碎的觉悟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算求饶也要撕咬嚼碎你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊 坂井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先自我介绍一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是“拾尸者”拉弥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所知是红世之徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你把夏娜打成那样的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我已通报了姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.05,0:15:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该是你自我介绍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘器少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫坂井悠二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井悠二啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.56,0:16:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了自己所处的境地后还能保持镇静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.66,0:16:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说只是对一切都死心了而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你提到夏娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.44,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在你身边的火雾战士吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.22,0:16:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜这名字是我取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.77,0:16:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她在一起的是“天壤劫火”阿拉斯托尔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 炎发灼眼的追捕者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就能避免不必要的战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.76,0:16:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必要？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你既然是徒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吞食人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如名所述 尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是只吞食火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.07,0:16:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只吞食那些已很微弱即将湮灭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.59,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身体也是为了不消耗存在之力而借用了火炬之躯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.25,0:17:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我创造出了达成目的的自在法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.17,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在收集发动它的存在之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.21,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为此而活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.00,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想亲眼目睹终将现形之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手触摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲自确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把这城市的火炬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.43,0:17:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是在采集微弱之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.18,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同是火炬的你不会感到好受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.76,0:17:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我并没打算一直做下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被厉害角色追杀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.17,0:17:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有不喜欢我的所作所为的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠扁哦 马可西亚斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.37,0:18:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 杀了你 剁烂你 撕咬嚼碎你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.34,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像认识乱吃我的火炬的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.48,0:18:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了那家伙是我们的猎物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的混蛋 拉弥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次别想避开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉弥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“拾尸者”拉弥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避火指环“湛蓝”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空嬉戏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为我会乖乖地让你逃走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是 那个也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上告诉我能喝到很多酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.07,0:19:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我安静舒服地睡觉的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这太不讲理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问的也问到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该道别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.19,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是与得到的情报同等的疑问 那我就回答一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算是疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.97,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这样为一个目的而活是种什么样的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.38,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对自身的存在即将湮灭毫无感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.92,0:20:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在会忘记我的人中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.50,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了夏娜这个会永远记得我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.86,0:20:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在你能说是以坂井悠二的身份在生活吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.59,0:20:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来只是火炬而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是火炬的你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.51,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说会永远记得你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样真的好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.43,0:21:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被记住的并不是现在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.71,0:21:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有吞食你是因为你的火炬还很明亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.55,0:21:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于在这城市秘密酝酿的危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这信息怎么利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由现在存在着的你决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法利亚格尼在打着坏主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.31,0:21:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭这城市的“都市吞噬”设置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.67,0:21:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市将毁灭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有一切都将湮灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.47,0:21:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同你自身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你周围的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.62,0:21:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有一切都将消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.08,0:22:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么疏远秘器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.91,0:22:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是两个火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连“拾尸者”拉弥也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.43,0:22:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划要更改了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.80,0:22:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但计划要付诸实践了 玛丽安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.53,0:22:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.54,0:22:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.29,0:22:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.65,0:22:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个即将湮灭的火炬而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.99,0:22:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将秘器...
